Name: Arcadia
Description: A mountainous region in the central part of the Peloponnese.

Name: Argolis
Description: A region known for its archaeological sites, including Mycenae and Epidaurus.

Name: Corinthia
Description: A region in northeastern Peloponnese, home to the famous Corinth Canal.

Name: Laconia
Description: A historic region known for Sparta and the Mani Peninsula.

Name: Messenia
Description: A region known for its olive oil, beaches, and the ancient city of Messene.

Name: Elis
Description: A region in western Peloponnese, home to the ancient site of Olympia.
